{
  "levelId": "block-04",
  "chapterId": "block-04",
  "worldId": "block",
  "title": "红石工坊：修复机关",
  "rewards": {
    "growthPoints": 5
  },
  "scenes": [
    {
      "sceneId": "workshop",
      "background": "assets/story/pixel-worlds-v1/scenes/block/block-04.webp",
      "lines": [
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "红石工坊里，机关门一会儿开、一会儿关。最后一枚星门晶石就在里面。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "这里就是红石工坊。我们先把“修复机关”记在地图上。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "我听到方块碰撞的声音，新的建造点就在前面。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "先找稳固的方块，再一步一步搭出安全的路线。",
          "character": "block_builder",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "activity",
          "activityType": "repair",
          "prompt": "把红石线接回发光的机关。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left",
          "actions": [
            {
              "label": "接上红石线",
              "feedback": "红色能量像小火车一样跑过机关。"
            },
            {
              "label": "按下启动按钮",
              "feedback": "机器发出咔咔声，门锁松开了。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "小小探险家完成了第一步，接上红石线让周围的线索变得清楚起来。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "看！刚才藏起来的线索露出来了。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "方块放稳后，藏在墙后的通道露出来了。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "把这段通道接到村子的道路上，伙伴们就能一起通过。",
          "character": "block_builder",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "记住这块特别的方块，它会成为下一座建筑的起点。",
          "character": "block_builder",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "‘工’字像一件工具，动手做一做，机关就会回应。",
          "character": "block_builder",
          "position": "right"
        }
      ],
      "sceneAssets": {
